title: American Horror Story Season 9 1984 Cast Promo
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: The way Emma is dressed, she has got to be the "Final Girl".
Looks like a lot of new blood because I can’t recognize most of them. Love the 80s theme.
This season is gonna be a darker version of Dead of Summer. I’m getting that vibe from it

I like how a certin actor when they first join the show will have a character that in wardrobe is them but the next season its a drastic change
Like season 5 with the countess and gaga  and season 8 with michael and cody

I think that Leslie Grossman will be the owner of the camp, like the Camp was closed down in the sixties-seventies after some horrible things went down, and Leslie just so happened to go there when she was a kid. And as an adult, she tried to recreate her favorite place by buying the camp and refurbishing it, but there are so many dark secrets in her past that will be revealed throughout the season.
